text: The Tomis Team Dobrogea Wind Farm is a wind farm under construction in the Dobrogea region of Romania. It will consist of an individual wind farm with 300 individual wind turbinesTomis Team va dezvolta cel mai mare parc eolian din Romania with a nominal output of around 2 MW which will deliver up to 600 MW of power, enough to power over 393,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$ 750 million. ==Related pages== *List of large wind farms ==References== Category:Wind farms Category:Buildings and structures in Romania
title: Tomis Team Dobrogea Wind Farm
